name: Experiment Or Die #87
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. How long ago would most of the things in my Cool Alphabet have been considered nerdy or lame? Considering the first Marvel movie to ever come out was Iron Man in 2008 and I don't even think he was considered cool in 2008. But oh how things have changed. Just goes to show you that you never know what will be considered cool... and in the crypto space a decade can pass in a few months. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
